{
  "stem": "1530.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you couldn't think that this is, really in a way, your death, the end of your life.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Even though I'm alive today, I think my life somehow ended at that moment, because I've never been normal since then.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had been so affected.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Depressed, going from one doctor to another for at least 40 years or 42 years, yes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's my--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they put us in this large, what they call Lager C.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they had these big rooms where there were only like wooden boxes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And each wooden box had to hold 12 of us, like we were into each other like-- not animals, because animals have some--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Some way to move.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just were fitted kind of into each other, 12 people in every one of those.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--think they had a thousand people in every lager.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were thousands of-- and there were I don't know how many in a lager.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We remained together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was definitely so because we had to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We made an agreement that we're going to try to stay together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Till the bitter end we did stay together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All that time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got there, these block altestes, who worked with the Germans, screamed, unheard of voices, you know, like very deep and very loud, if you're not going to do this or that, you going to go up.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do you see that smoke?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's where your mother is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you're going to go up in that smoke.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How could you believe that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You-- I mean, you're coming from-- not just two months ago, I was in my home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you-- you just don't know who you are, don't know where you are.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
